divs: Sighting DetailsWent out on deck to have cigarette, just looking around, saw red and blue lights over the trees. It was just hanging there, could see it looked circular and had 4-5 lights. Was a dark gray color. It sat there for a minute or two and a bright blue and white beam came down in the middle of it and it just disappeared, no sound. Never say anything like it.
Summary: circular craft over tree tops, had red and blue lights
